{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act4d0_level_act4d0_st02","storyGroup":"act4d0","storySort":2,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"","storyName":"破局者","storyPic":"storyMainPic_level_act4d0_st02","storyInfo":"W带队拦截佣兵队伍中的叛逃者，在冲突后，炎客突围离开整合运动。\n而来到罗德岛的炎客，将会遇见另一位故人。\n","storyCanEnter":0,"storyTxt":"activities/act4d0/level_act4d0_st02","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"USE_ITEM","costItemType":"MATERIAL","costItemId":"STORY_REVIEW_COIN","costItemCount":1,"stageCount":0,"requiredStages":[],"prev":0,"next":2,"characters":["整合运动术师","W","整合运动刀兵","？？？","炎客","杜宾"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第一关（前）","id":0},{"type":"Dialog","id":1},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":2},{"type":"Character","id":3},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","delay":"0.5","id":4,"musicid":0},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.4","id":5},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"W，我们遇到了点麻烦。","id":6},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"嚯......值得你们用这个频道联系我，怎么？发现了什么有趣的事情？","id":7},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"不太有趣，W，在你重整那些萨卡兹雇佣兵的时候，有一支队伍叛逃了。","id":8},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"好像是支负责清扫战场的后勤队伍，所以我们直接发起了追击。","id":9},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"意料之内的，他们变成了一盘散沙，一触即溃，开始向城外撤离。","id":10},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"可喜可贺。","id":11},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"但，意料之外的情况是......我们派去追击的小队，和我们失去了联系。","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"作为佣兵们的新领头人，希望你能给出合理的解释。","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"我们的小队为什么人间蒸发了？","id":14},{"type":"Dialog","id":15},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_cher_3","width":"1","height":"1","fadetime":"1","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"Text","text":"01:13 P.M.    天气/晴","id":17},{"type":"Text","text":"切尔诺伯格，郊外，荒野","id":18},{"type":"Dialog","id":19},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":20},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"这种描述可不利于我理解喔？","id":22,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Character","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"事实如此。协同小队没发现埋伏和陷阱，只知道敌人是萨卡兹人。","id":24},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"那自然是萨卡兹了，我的佣兵还能有什么其他种族呢？不过，挺有趣的。接着说。","id":26,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Character","id":27},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"最先接触的时候，目标被成功压制，出于谨慎，追击小队也有所保留。对方并不是什么强敌。","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"然而某个时刻，通讯突然中断了。","id":29},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"......嗯，比起你们，真正的野兽更善于隐藏自己的尖牙利齿，你们这也太大意了吧。","id":31,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Character","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"我们该怎么办？","id":33},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"那些萨卡兹人有什么特点？","id":35,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Character","id":36},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"......不清楚，目击者大都失去了联络。从远处看，只知道有一名近身陷阵的战士。","id":37},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"那就不要和他们正面接触。拖住那个人，我们一会见。","id":39,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.4","id":40},{"type":"Dialog","id":41},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":42},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":43},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"出了什么事？","id":44,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_1002_nsabr_2","focus":"1","id":45},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"没什么，只是有一支不够成熟的小队中了诱饵。","id":46,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_1002_nsabr_2","focus":"2","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"我们要去支援他们吗？","id":48,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","name2":"char_1002_nsabr_2","focus":"1","id":49},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"唉，明明大家都有自己的工作，为什么不能各自处理好分内的事情呢？","id":50,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"嗯......不过这次就不深究了吧。毕竟我也非常在意我可怜的前领导带着哪些奇怪的萨卡兹人呢。","id":51,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","name2":"char_1002_nsabr_2","focus":"2","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"明白了。","id":53,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":54},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"通知全体小队，临战整备，转移到城郊。","id":55,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","volume":"0.5","id":56},{"type":"Dialog","id":57},{"type":"Character","id":58},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":59},{"type":"Character","id":60},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.4","id":61},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$calamity_intro","key":"$calamity_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","delay":"0.5","id":62,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":63},{"type":"character","id":64},{"type":"Dialog","id":65},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":66},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":67},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":68},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":69},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":70},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":71},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":72},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":73},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":74},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_wizard_1","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"呃，该死，这家伙的动作又变快了！他还在隐藏实力吗？","id":76,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"character","id":77},{"type":"Dialog","id":78},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":80},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":81},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":82},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#7","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......太弱小了，所谓的整合运动只有这种水平吗？","id":84,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5#7"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_wizard_1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"你这家伙！竟然小看我们——","id":86,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":87},{"type":"Character","id":88},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":89},{"type":"Character","id":90},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.4","id":91},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"呵......","id":95,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"本来就预想到会遇上几个老熟人，可没想到会是你啊。","id":96,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_wizard_1","id":97},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"W，我们——","id":98,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"1","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"归队，除非你想送死。别摆出那副急着报仇的表情，他还没有使出全力。哦，想送死的话，我就不拦着你咯？","id":100,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"2","id":101},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"......收队。","id":102,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":103},{"type":"character","id":104},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":105},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#4","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":106},{"type":"Delay","time":"3","id":107},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"很久不见了，佣兵刀术师。","id":109,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":110},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"你——","id":111,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":112},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"现在，叫我W。","id":113,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"你呢？","id":114,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"炎客。你应该明白，于我而言，互报姓名的意义。","id":116,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"哎呀，可怕可怕，过去你手刃那些家伙的时候，也会互报姓名吗？","id":118,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"委托和厮杀是不一样的。","id":120,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":121},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"作为一个经历过那场战争的萨卡兹人忽然销声匿迹，很令人担心啊。","id":122,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"佣兵嘛，只不过是换了个领头人就要跑路，让人很心慌喔？","id":123,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"这无关紧要。","id":125,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"不过没想到，你的部下连让我报上名字的价值都没有。","id":126,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"那还真是荣幸......嗯，虽然他们成为我部下也没多长时间。啊，你是在邀请我杀了你？","id":128,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"不，我对你仰仗外力的战斗方式毫无兴趣。","id":130,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"但我得承认，战术也是一种技巧。如果你的战术比过去更加精湛，我愿意领教。","id":131,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"......奇怪，你过去不是那种“只要杀了目标怎么都好”的类型吗？","id":133,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":134},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"W，小队已经分散到了指定点，已经彻底切断了敌人的退路，他逃不掉的。","id":135,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"我也没想到你能成为这些家伙的领导者，大家都在改变。","id":137,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"这些家伙？啊......你是说整合运动？","id":139,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"还是说......萨卡兹们？","id":140,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":141},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"喝——！","id":142,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":143},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#2","id":144},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":145},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":146},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":147},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":148},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.6","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"唔。","id":150,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#2","name2":"char_1002_nsabr_2","focus":"2","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"我是不会轻敌的，萨卡兹人，我注意你很久了。","id":152,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"很可惜，你没有机会钻空子。","id":153,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#4","name2":"char_1002_nsabr_2","focus":"1","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"原来如此，你也是......","id":155,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"这不是有意思多了吗，你能作为砥石为我所用吗？我的刀有些钝了。","id":156,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#4","name2":"char_1002_nsabr_2","focus":"2","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"挑衅？你也就现在能嚣张两下了！","id":158,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#4","name2":"char_1002_nsabr_2","focus":"1","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"嗯，来吧。","id":160,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":161},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#4","id":162},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":163},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":164},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":165},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":167},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":168},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":169},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":170},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":171},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":172},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":173},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":174},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"唔呃！该死！你是怎么——","id":176,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":177},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":178},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":179},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":180},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"呃——！","id":182,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#4","id":183},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"你还有空说话吗？","id":184,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":185},{"type":"Character","id":186},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":187},{"type":"Character","id":188},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.4","id":189},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"......意料之内，他变得更强了。","id":192,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"2","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"W！我们为什么就站在这里看着！？只要你下令，他立刻就会灰飞烟灭了！","id":194,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"1","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"所以现在，我又能对你发号施令了？","id":196,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"2","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"别在这种时候找茬！","id":198,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"但我确实不是你们的指挥官呀。","id":200,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"提个建议，收手吧，别刺激他了，自找麻烦最好换个时间。","id":202,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":203},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":204},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":205},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":206},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":207},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":208},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"......该死。","id":209,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"不是吧？你难道真的打算单打独斗就解决他？别在这里搞笑啊。","id":211,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"嘁。","id":213,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":214},{"type":"character","id":215},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":216},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#2","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":217},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"下一个是谁？","id":219,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5#2","focus":"1","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"这么着急，是赶着去赴谁的约吗？","id":221,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"我不是第一次杀出重围了。","id":223,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"唔，嗯，原来如此。我想，你大概是在说内战时候的事吧？我有点兴趣，能说说吗？","id":225,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"没什么。被人埋伏，所有人死了而我还活着，就这么简单。","id":227,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"怎么样？还要继续吗？","id":228,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"对我来说，刚才的战斗还远远不够。","id":229,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":230},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"不......我在想，也许你应该加入我们。","id":231,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_wizard_1","id":232},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"W！？他这个叛逃者，已经杀了那么多整合运动的——","id":233,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#1","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"1","id":234},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"是我的佣兵们决定要用他，整合运动需要他。有意见？","id":235,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#1","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"你！","id":237,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#1","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":238},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"......","id":239,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"不管怎么想，都是我们这边更有趣吧？战争，流血，还有那么多萨卡兹同僚......","id":241,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"你追求的一切在这里都是打折大放送哦。","id":242,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"当然，这份邀请也出于我个人的好奇心，我们一定有很多共同话题。","id":243,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":244},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"我不这么认为。","id":245,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":246},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"你也是感染者吧？加入整合运动又有什么不好呢？","id":247,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":248},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"无序的破坏，带着某种目的的集团暴行，我看不出能从这样的组织里得到什么。","id":249,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"战争？现在的你们不过是摩擦迸发出的点点火种，你应该知道真正的战争是什么样的。","id":250,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"别这么说，我们也是有在努力工作的，何况整合运动之间也有区别嘛。","id":252,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"虽然我的前任上司喜欢更纯粹些的东西，但我可是无论什么都乐在其中啊。","id":253,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":254},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"如果非要说的话......是呢，我想领教一下塔露拉的剑术。","id":255,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"那个龙女？虽然我不想称赞她，但你基本没有一丁点胜算喔。","id":257,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"而且她那个，能算剑术吗？你在靠近她之前就会变成一块炭吧？","id":258,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":259},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"我知道。","id":260,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"当然，我也知道，如果我拒绝你的条件，我突围的机会同样小之又小。","id":261,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"可这又何妨？只有在令人窒息的枷锁中挣脱，我才有可能更进一步。","id":262,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#5","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":263},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"你......什么时候变得这么有情调了？","id":264,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#5","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":265},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"我只是在寻求自己活着的意义。","id":266,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":267},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"好吧，随你怎么说。不要管那个龙女了，单纯加入佣兵队伍如何？","id":268,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"老工作的话，你也能更加得心应手吧。再说了，你不喜欢的上司，已经死了哦。","id":269,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":270},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"你并不值得信任。你我都互相隐瞒了很多事情。","id":271,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"......呵，有一个很不错的地方，那里比整合运动更适合磨砺我的刀刃。","id":272,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"我看到了。不久之前，我看到你和那个外来的萨卡兹人交易的场面。但除此之外，他们的战斗令我心动。","id":273,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#5","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"还有这种事？！","id":275,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#5","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"就算他最后被你除掉了，事实就是事实，依然在那里。遮掩是没用的。","id":277,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":278},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"唔。","id":279,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"真是败给你啦！行啦行啦。我确实和他口头约定好，让他干掉我的上司，方便我去做事呢。","id":280,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"毕竟大家也是老相识了嘛，面子也是要卖一个的。","id":281,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":282},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"但你不可能放过他们。","id":283,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":284},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"至少我放过了他想保护的人啊。","id":285,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"我答应他，会给罗德岛的救援队提供帮助——这和我杀死他这件事，也没什么矛盾吧？","id":286,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"再说了，我也有自己的规划，钓线总要放长一些才行。但手上的猎物，也没理由让他跑了。","id":287,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#4","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"就算这样，他也消灭了你好不容易弄到手的精英战士。","id":289,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":290},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"够了！这事，我可还是很生气的！","id":291,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"唉。难得遇到一位旧识，本来还以为能搞好关系，最后还是你死我活，我也很伤心的。","id":292,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1002_nsabr_2","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动刀兵","text":"......W，我们必须动手了。拖得太久会影响既定的计划。","id":294,"figure":"char_1002_nsabr_2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":295},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"好啦，既然大家时间都很紧迫......你真的不打算改变你的看法？","id":296,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":297},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"自然不会。","id":298,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":299},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"最后一个问题，你现在的雇主是谁？啊，抱歉，反正你是不会说的吧。","id":300,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"但我大致猜得到。","id":301,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":302},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"是吗，我以为他们没有那么有名。","id":303,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"我有不少旧识在那里。欸，虽然我的旧识到处都是啦，你也算是呢。","id":305,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"前言不搭后语。","id":307,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"不，我要说的是，我也许清楚一些你以前的佣兵队伍被消灭的内幕。","id":309,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"尊敬的刀术师队长，策划了那次的阴谋，让你变成现在这样子的人，说不定就在你要去的地方哦？","id":310,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#3","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":311},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"是吗？","id":312,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"是吗......","id":313,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"有趣。","id":314,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#5","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":315},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"啊哈哈，原来你不知道！当然了，我也是刚刚才知道。","id":316,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"很快你就会发现，事情肯定没你想的那么简单。","id":317,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"我很期待你会怎么做，呵呵，你总会做些什么的。","id":318,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#5","name2":"char_1011_wizard_1","focus":"2","id":319},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"整合运动术师","text":"W！你还要等到什么时候！？","id":320,"figure":"char_1011_wizard_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5","id":321},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"......","id":322,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw#1","id":323},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"哎，说真的，我的萨卡兹们不会动手哦？要干活，你们自己去干。","id":324,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"刀术师——不，炎客，在之后的战斗里，你可能会死。","id":325,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw#1"},{"type":"dialog","id":326},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":327},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":328},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_ac4_1","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","id":329},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":330},{"type":"ImageTween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"0","xTo":"0","yTo":"-20","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.1","yScaleTo":"1.1","duration":"15","block":"false","id":331},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"久违的死局。我很兴奋。","id":332},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"久违的？这么说来，也许你佣兵队的全灭并没让你变得冷酷，反而让你变得快乐起来了？","id":333},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"我和你没有相像之处，W，快乐不是值得追求的目标。","id":334},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"“上一次”让我失去了很多东西，但我眼前的道路却变得明晰而清澈。","id":335},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"这一次，希望你们不要让我失望。","id":336},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"你居然在笑哎。","id":337},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"如果我说这次会饶你一命，你信吗？","id":338},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"我，也想这么问。","id":339},{"type":"dialog","id":340},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":341},{"type":"Image","fadetime":"0","id":342},{"type":"Background","id":343},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":344},{"type":"Dialog","id":345},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":346},{"type":"Character","id":347},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":348},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":349},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":350},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":351},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":352},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$e_skill_skulsrsword","volume":"0.9","id":353},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":354},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":355},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":356},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":357},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":358},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":359},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":360},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":361},{"type":"Delay","time":"3","id":362},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_bridge","screenadapt":"coverall","id":363},{"type":"Character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","id":364},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":365},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$tech_intro","key":"$tech_loop","volume":"0.6","crossfade":"1.5","delay":"0.5","id":366,"musicid":2},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"合同内容——似乎没有要求你在正式登舰前，就和整合运动正面冲突。","id":367,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":368},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"是我个人的原因。","id":369,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":370},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"我们欢迎感染者和有志于解决感染者问题的各类人才，但绝不接纳违反规则和条例的人。","id":371,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"鉴于我们并不知道当时的具体情况，就不把这件事纳入考察了。","id":372,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"下不为例。","id":373,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":374},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"如果有必要，就按你们的方式处理。","id":375,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":376},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"我们已经处理过了。你的动机和个人诉求，我们不会纳入考量——不如说。","id":377,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"如果判断你是罗德岛无法接纳的人，那么即使你既高尚又正直，我们也不能网开一面。","id":378,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":379},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"是的，仅仅是我的个人诉求。","id":380,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":381},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"哼，不管这个，欢迎来到罗德岛。","id":382,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"这么说吧，你的行为每时每刻，都会影响到身边干员，身边的干员也会针对你的行为作出决策。","id":383,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"只要你遵守规则，罗德岛会十分宽容地对待你，无论你的过去怎么样。","id":384,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"相反，听着，干员炎客，只要你做出哪怕一丁点出格的事情......","id":385,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"2","id":386},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"唔。","id":387,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_130_doberm_ex","name2":"char_131_flameb_5","focus":"1","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜宾","text":"接下来，我领你去医疗部门吧，有个人想见见你。","id":389,"figure":"char_130_doberm_ex"},{"type":"Dialog","id":390},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":391},{"type":"character","id":392},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":393},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_corridor","screenadapt":"coverall","id":394},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":395},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":396},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#3","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":397},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":398},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"400","text":"——你是？"}],"values":[],"id":399},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":400},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5","id":401},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"......","id":402,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"你......","id":403,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5"},{"type":"Decision","options":[{"id":"405","text":"抱歉，借过。"}],"values":[],"id":404},{"type":"Predicate","references":["1"],"id":405},{"type":"character","id":406},{"type":"Dialog","id":407},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":408},{"type":"Delay","time":"3","id":409},{"type":"Character","name":"char_131_flameb_5#4","id":410},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"......呵。","id":411,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"真是这样。","id":412,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"W，你还真是诚实啊......","id":413,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎客","text":"看来活久一点，确实有些益处。","id":414,"figure":"char_131_flameb_5#4"},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":415},{"type":"Dialog","id":416},{"type":"Blocker","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":417},{"type":"Image","id":418}],"characters":["整合运动术师","W","整合运动刀兵","？？？","炎客","杜宾"]}